{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01EmFPpS3cqeaVt1NiiwSee4","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# ULTRAPLAN Contract Spec (Rust)\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Objective\n4\t\n5\tDefine Rust rewrite contracts for ULTRAPLAN launch and remote planning lifecycle with explicit orphan-prevention and concurrency rules.\n6\t\n7\t## 2. Evidence Anchors (Current Code)\n8\t\n9\t1. Command registration gate: `commands.ts:104`\n10\t2. Keyword auto-route: `utils/processUserInput/processUserInput.ts:468`\n11\t3. Launch flow and teleport call: `commands/ultraplan.tsx:330`\n12\t4. Error-path archive cleanup: `commands/ultraplan.tsx:395`\n13\t5. Concurrent launch/poll guard: `commands/ultraplan.tsx:264`\n14\t6. Plan-mode permission UI integration: `components/permissions/ExitPlanModePermissionRequest/ExitPlanModePermissionRequest.tsx:144`\n15\t7. Polling approval flow: `commands/ultraplan.tsx:83`\n16\t\n17\t## 3. Rust Ownership Boundaries\n18\t\n19\t1. `crates/api-types`\n20\tUltraplan state, poll phase, launch/stop result contracts.\n21\t2. `crates/app-services`\n22\tUltraplan orchestration and state machine policy.\n23\t3. `crates/remote-runtime`\n24\tRemote session creation, polling, archive transport.\n25\t4. `crates/config`\n26\tTimeout defaults, gate keys, model defaults.\n27\t5. `bins/app-cli`\n28\tCommand wiring and user messaging.\n29\t6. `crates/ui-tui`\n30\tInteractive prompt/permission view state only.\n31\t\n32\t## 4. State Machine\n33\t\n34\tStates:\n35\t\n36\t1. `Idle`\n37\t2. `Launching`\n38\t3. `Polling`\n39\t4. `AwaitingInput`\n40\t5. `Approved`\n41\t6. `Stopping`\n42\t7. `Completed`\n43\t8. `Failed`\n44\t\n45\tAllowed transitions:\n46\t\n47\t1. `Idle -> Launching`\n48\t2. `Launching -> Polling | Failed`\n49\t3. `Polling -> AwaitingInput | Approved | Failed | Stopping`\n50\t4. `AwaitingInput -> Polling | Stopping`\n51\t5. `Approved -> Completed`\n52\t6. `Stopping -> Completed | Failed`\n53\t\n54\tTerminal: `Completed`, `Failed`\n55\t\n56\t## 5. Proposed Contracts (Rust)\n57\t\n58\t```rust\n59\tuse serde::{Deserialize, Serialize};\n60\tuse std::time::Duration;\n61\t\n62\t#[derive(Debug, Clone, Serialize, Deserialize, PartialEq, Eq)]\n63\tpub enum UltraplanPhase {\n64\t    Idle,\n65\t    Launching,\n66\t    Polling,\n67\t    AwaitingInput,\n68\t    Approved,\n69\t    Stopping,\n70\t    Completed,\n71\t    Failed,\n72\t}\n73\t\n74\t#[derive(Debug, Clone, Serialize, Deserialize)]\n75\tpub struct UltraplanSession {\n76\t    pub session_id: String,\n77\t    pub session_url: String,\n78\t    pub phase: UltraplanPhase,\n79\t}\n80\t\n81\t#[derive(Debug, Clone, Copy)]\n82\tpub struct UltraplanPolicy {\n83\t    pub timeout: Duration,\n84\t    pub single_active_session: bool,\n85\t}\n86\t```\n87\t\n88\t```rust\n89\t#[async_trait::async_trait]\n90\tpub trait UltraplanService: Send + Sync {\n91\t    async fn launch(&self, prompt: &str, policy: UltraplanPolicy) -> Result<UltraplanSession, UltraplanError>;\n92\t    async fn poll(&self, session_id: &str) -> Result<UltraplanPhase, UltraplanError>;\n93\t    async fn stop(&self, session_id: &str) -> Result<(), UltraplanError>;\n94\t    async fn archive_orphan(&self, session_id: &str) -> Result<(), UltraplanError>;\n95\t}\n96\t```\n97\t\n98\t## 6. Policy Rules\n99\t\n100\t1. At most one active ULTRAPLAN session per local session context.\n101\t2. Launch attempts while `Launching/Polling` return deterministic concurrency error.\n102\t3. If failure happens after remote session creation, archive must be attempted.\n103\t4. Stop operation clears local active session marker before returning.\n104\t5. Keyword auto-route must respect launch/polling guards.\n105\t\n106\t## 7. Error Taxonomy\n107\t\n108\t```rust\n109\t#[derive(thiserror::Error, Debug)]\n110\tpub enum UltraplanError {\n111\t    #[error(\"feature disabled by policy\")]\n112\t    DisabledByPolicy,\n113\t    #[error(\"already active\")]\n114\t    AlreadyActive,\n115\t    #[error(\"launch failed\")]\n116\t    LaunchFailed,\n117\t    #[error(\"poll timeout\")]\n118\t    PollTimeout,\n119\t    #[error(\"approval failed\")]\n120\t    ApprovalFailed,\n121\t    #[error(\"archive failed\")]\n122\t    ArchiveFailed,\n123\t    #[error(\"transport error: {0}\")]\n124\t    Transport(String),\n125\t}\n126\t```\n127\t\n128\t## 8. Constants Classification\n129\t\n130\t1. `api-types`: phase enums and lifecycle event names.\n131\t2. `config`: launch timeout, poll interval, gate keys, model defaults.\n132\t3. `core-domain`: transition invariants for ultraplan phase graph.\n133\t4. `remote-runtime`: endpoint path and transport retry constants.\n134\t5. `ui-tui`: usage/help strings.\n135\t\n136\t## 9. Acceptance Test Matrix\n137\t\n138\t### 9.1 Contract tests\n139\t\n140\t1. Invalid phase transition rejected.\n141\t2. Concurrent launch attempt returns `AlreadyActive`.\n142\t3. Stop/cleanup from active state transitions deterministically.\n143\t\n144\t### 9.2 Integration tests\n145\t\n146\t1. Launch -> Poll -> Approved -> Completed happy path.\n147\t2. Launch success + downstream failure triggers orphan archive attempt.\n148\t3. Poll timeout path returns `PollTimeout`.\n149\t\n150\t### 9.3 CLI behavior tests\n151\t\n152\t1. Bare command usage path returns expected guidance.\n153\t2. Keyword-trigger while active does not re-launch.\n154\t3. Stop command clears local active markers and session URL state.\n155\t\n156\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01XcwKb2RbRK1ZWthDdBWymB","session_id":"c8641186-7fb9-40c9-80e2-66e2f0b1f59f","uuid":"1593a483-db65-4dfd-b2bf-c8e9620dac8c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:42:53.853Z"}
